headline: Biden Clashes With Senator On How Trial Plays in Iowa
abstract: As Mr. Biden campaigned in the state, residents appeared unmoved: “I don’t think much about anything Joni Ernst says.”
lead_paragraph: MUSCATINE, Iowa — Senator Joni Ernst of Iowa, a Republican, wondered aloud about her Democratic constituents as they wrestled with a final decision before the looming Iowa caucuses, particularly those considering supporting former Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr.
keywords: Trump-Ukraine Whistle-blower Complaint and Impeachment Inquiry
